Package com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps

com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps contains all functionalities of the enterprise service. Provided functionalities are creating, updating and deletion of portfolios and portfolio classes. The portfolio classes can be grouped in a tree structure and mHealthAtlas application can be mapped to a portfolio class. Additionally application can be annotated.
